01:07:21,709 --> 01:07:22,520
¿Sí?

1165
01:07:22,544 --> 01:07:23,453
<i>¿Doctor Brower?</i>

1166
01:07:23,477 --> 01:07:24,388
<i>Habla Jane Williams,</i>

1167
01:07:24,412 --> 01:07:26,122
<i>secretaria del Comité
